title: Jono Love Me Love My Face 2010 PDTV x264-CBFM
description:
Jono Love Me Love My Face 2010 PDTV x264-CBFM

the inspirational story of Jono Lancaster who was born with a rare genetic condition, Treacher Collins Syndrome. This affected the way his facial bones developed and he was given up for adoption after he was born. In the programme, we follow Jono as he searches for his birth parents and sets out to prove that the syndrome doesn't define him or his life.
